result.name: Tsui Wah

html_attributions: ธารเทพ จงจิตร

reviews.text: nice food, but doesn't have enough waiter, waitress
Nothing could go wrong with this egg tarts ! Crispy outside juicy inside. Just give it a try la
Good service, speedy delivery, relatively cheap.

Today it is Chinese new year  ( 5th Feb )and it isn't really the best day to go there. Why I am saying this is because as you all know in the new years thousands or even millions of tourists rampage through the streets to get to Wong Tai Sin Temple to worship the god for good luck and fortune, as you can tell that is a LOT of people around so why not stop at Tsui Wah to get a nice tea break from that humongous crowd? If you are thinking that the prices are going to be cheaper you are wrong, the prices have not changed and you need to wait like a time that feels like forever just to get a table for even just 2. The food by the way, just more worse than a normal afternoon at this restaurant, pork chop was harder than ever and there isn't enough sauce on it to feed a ant! The rice was ok but the fries are not even fries! Just grilled potato sticks, so I'll just give it a big fat 2 star.
Usually I don't mind this chain, but staff seemed a bit unprofessional when I went here last time.

reviews.text: Consistently good food with a wide selection of vegetarian as well as meat and fish based dishes. Perfect for mixed group of meat eaters and vegetarians.

Scrambled egg is particularly delicious, and the soup is not as oily as other Chinese restaurant in European countries; steaming is not suitable style for frozen fish, pan-fried fish may be better way
Restaurant is cozy and nice decor . I find the food is average . Service is good ! Good for quick meal and catch up with friends .
Bad first impression with this dipping noodles. Very different from the picture in the menu, couldn't even find any crab meat. Does not worth the price, would never order this again.
Average price, average food, fast and big portion

result.name: 上海廳1930

reviews.text: 坐位好窄.食物ㄧ般.味道普通.無上海本幫菜風味。扮曬野。價錢都不相而。
全部野都難食都傻，難食到要特登上黎比分，現成整定再翻熱
交通便利，坐位多，寬敞，服務ok ，價錢中上，食物質素幾好， 上海菜當然要試小籠包，生煎包，担担麵，味道算ok 但唔係我食過最好的。
座位舒適，服務也可以。但味道一1般
地点在黄大仙屋邨人流太雜，商場太細停車場亦細，最敗筆是要走一大段路及要通通八度防火門才能到達商場，加上食物無甚驚喜，但價錢亦不貴，如有腳骨力者不妨一試。

result.name: 翠華餐廳

html_attributions: ธารเทพ จงจิตร

reviews.text: 웡타이신 사원 갔다가 밥먹으러 간곳. 어디갈지 고민하다가 그냥 넓길래 감... Afternoon tea set(오후 2시반~6시, 일요일은 x, 토요일 o)가 있는데 나쁘지 않았습니다. A,B,D 먹었는데 A는 나쁘진 않으나 국물맛이 약간 입맛에 따라 별로라고 느낄수도..(해산물 베이스 국물 싫어하시면 비추.) B는 위에 올라간 닭날개는 향신료맛이 살짝 나도 먹을순 있었습니다 하지만 면 소스는 닭보다 향신료 향이 살짝 나서 혹시 향신료는 좋아하지 않으나 매운걸 좋아하시면 비치되어있는 칠리 오일을 뿌려서 비벼드심 매워져서 먹기 괜찮습니다. 매운게 향신료를 잊게해줌. 오일의 맵기는 불닭수준.. D는 가장 무난하게 먹을수 있고 고기는 돼지갈비찜을 아주 연하게 조린 맛이고 국물은 연한 돼지갈비찜에 사발면 사리 넣어먹는 느낌입니다 그냥저냥 먹을만... 총 4가지에 4명 차값 해서 128달라였었...
去個幾次，近來去食下午茶，鮮油波羅加熱飲只是26元杯熱飲好大杯.
餐廳入口處販賣的叉燒包和腸仔包便宜又好吃，餐廳菜色的選擇也多，價格也還算平價。

湯底比我想像中好
